    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Absolute showstopper alert! This vehicle is in genuine mint condition \u2014 and it truly lives up to that description. The exterior is flawless, with paint that gleams brilliantly and not a scratch, chip, or blemish in sight. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 every surface, seat, and detail looks and feels brand new. Under the hood, everything is in perfect working order, running smoothly and powerfully just as it should. This is the kind of car you rarely come across in the used market, and it's an opportunity you won't want to miss! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 47500.0,
