      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move! \ud83d\udd27 This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it's a well-worn car that will require some attention and repairs to get it running at its best. The exterior shows significant signs of wear including noticeable scratches, dents, and fading paint. The interior reflects heavy use and will need some TLC. Mechanically, the car has known issues that a buyer should be prepared to address. That said, this could be a great opportunity for a handy buyer, a DIY mechanic, or someone looking for an affordable parts vehicle. Sold as-is \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects that honestly!",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we want to be upfront with all potential buyers about what to expect. The car is fully functional and drivable, making it a practical option for budget-conscious buyers who don't mind some imperfections. The exterior shows visible wear beyond typical use \u2014 expect scratches, minor dents, and some fading on the paint. The interior has noticeable wear on the seats, dashboard, and trim, reflecting years of regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but may require some attention in the near term \u2014 we recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you can plan accordingly. This is an honest, straightforward offering for a buyer who wants reliable transportation without paying for a pristine vehicle.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in exceptional mint condition \u2014 quite simply one of the finest examples you'll find on the used market. The exterior is virtually flawless, with paint that retains a deep, rich shine and absolutely no meaningful scratches, dents, or blemishes to report. Body panels are perfectly aligned, and all trim, glass, and lighting components are in pristine shape. Inside, the cabin looks and smells nearly new \u2014 upholstery is spotless, all surfaces are unmarked, and every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights. Service history is well-maintained, and the mechanical components are in excellent working order throughout. Tires have substantial tread remaining, and brakes are in great shape. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle that truly feels like new \u2014 ideal for a buyer who wants the best without paying new-car prices.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in fair condition \u2014 an honest designation that reflects a car with noticeable wear and some issues that a prospective buyer should be aware of going in. The exterior shows its age, with visible scratches, minor dents, and paint fading or oxidation in several areas. The interior is functional but worn \u2014 expect scuffed surfaces, some tears or staining in the upholstery, and general signs of heavy use over the years. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it is not without its quirks; buyers should anticipate some deferred maintenance items and potentially a repair or two down the road. This is a solid candidate for a budget-conscious buyer who is handy with repairs, needs reliable basic transportation, or is looking for a project vehicle. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged so you know exactly what you're getting. Priced accordingly to reflect the current condition honestly.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    }
